<div class="faq-page">
  <div class="faq-wrapper">
    <div class="faq-header">
      <h1 class="faq-title">FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS</h1>
      <p class="faq-subtitle">Everything you need to know</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-list">
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3 class="faq-question">What are pheromone fragrances?</h3>
        <p class="faq-answer">Pheromone fragrances are scientifically crafted scents that enhance your natural chemistry. Our elite blends are designed to boost confidence and create lasting impressions through a combination of premium fragrance notes and scientifically-proven pheromone compounds.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3 class="faq-question">How long does shipping take?</h3>
        <p class="faq-answer">We ship via USPS Parcel Select. Standard delivery is 3-5 business days within the continental United States. Orders over $75 ship free. International shipping available upon request.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3 class="faq-question">What's your return policy?</h3>
        <p class="faq-answer">We stand behind our products with a 30-day money-back guarantee. If you're not completely satisfied with your purchase, contact our team within 30 days of delivery for a full refund. Product must be at least 75% full to qualify for return.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3 class="faq-question">How should I apply the fragrance?</h3>
        <p class="faq-answer">Apply 2-3 sprays to pulse points: wrists, neck, and chest. The warmth of these areas helps diffuse the scent throughout the day. For best results, apply to clean, moisturized skin. Avoid rubbing wrists together as this breaks down the fragrance molecules.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3 class="faq-question">Can I layer different scents?</h3>
        <p class="faq-answer">Each scent is designed to stand alone as a complete fragrance experience. We recommend choosing one signature scent per occasion for maximum impact and projection. However, advanced users can experiment with layering complementary notes.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3 class="faq-question">How long will a bottle last?</h3>
        <p class="faq-answer">With normal usage (2-3 sprays per day), a 50ml bottle lasts approximately 2-3 months, while a 100ml bottle lasts 4-6 months. Our high concentration ensures you need fewer sprays than typical designer fragrances.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3 class="faq-question">Are your fragrances suitable for sensitive skin?</h3>
        <p class="faq-answer">Our fragrances are formulated with premium ingredients and undergo rigorous testing. However, if you have sensitive skin, we recommend testing on a small area first. All ingredients are listed on each product page.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3 class="faq-question">Do you offer wholesale or bulk pricing?</h3>
        <p class="faq-answer">Yes, we offer special pricing for bulk orders and retail partnerships. Contact our team at wholesale@neversettle.com for more information on minimum order quantities and pricing tiers.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "FAQ Page"
}
{% endschema %}
